milestones.description: Sese Bau has broken the record for most ducks (3) in ODIs for PNG, going past Norman Vanua's 2
Jack Vare has broken the record for most dismissals (9) in ODIs for PNG, going past Dogodo Bau's 7
This is the lowest match aggregate (334) involving teams P.N.G. & U.A.E. in ODIs
U.A.E.'s 108-run win against P.N.G. is the largest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 103-run win against P.N.G.
Vani Morea has scored 3 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for PNG breaking Mahuru Dai's record
Rameez Shahzad has scored 1 hundreds in ODIs, the most for UAE breaking Khurram Khan's record
Naveed has broken the record for most sixes (12) in ODIs for UAE, going past Shaiman Anwar's 12
Mahuru Dai has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (15) for PNG, going past Tony Ura
